<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div><div><div><div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">At BSKL we review our Security Policy regularly and would like to remind you of the school security procedures, and ask for your support by wearing your ID Tags at all times.</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">&nbsp;</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial;"><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">The control of visitors is fundamental for the safeguarding of both people and property in the school. Our policy regarding visitors to the school is that:&nbsp;</font></div><div><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">All visitors arriving by car not displaying a BSKL sticker must provide identification at the security gate. The security guards will confirm with Reception that visitors are expected by a member of staff.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Once confirmed as bona fide, these visitors must report to the reception desk on arrival.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">If there is any doubt about a visitor’s identity, or their reason for attempting to gain access to the school, security guards will contact a member of the school leadership team.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">All visitors are issued with a visitor’s ID tag to be worn at all times. This includes family and friends of parents, helpers, contractors, and any other person who is not employed by the school.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Any person on site without a badge will be asked to accompany a member of staff to the reception desk or asked to leave the site.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Any refusal will be reported immediately to the Head Teacher. Any aggression will be reported to the police.&nbsp;</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">The school reserves the right to search visitors' cars and baggage and to screen visitors with a metal detector.</font></li></ul></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Additional measures are put in place during times of high alert:</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><ul><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Local police organise increased patrols along Changkat Bukit Utama and the school car parks.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Extra security guards are deployed and are on high alert.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Cars with no stickers and no registered appointment will not be allowed on site.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">The school will liaise directly with the British and US Embassies to ensure we are apprised of the most up to date security advice.</font></li><li><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">We are also in direct communication with the Regional Police who are supporting our security procedures.&nbsp;</font></li></ul></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Your support with these procedures is much appreciated.</font></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Regards,</font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Janet Brock</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div><b><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">Headteacher</font></b></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div></div></span></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
